Module FlightBookingSystem_Dist
Package bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model

Class Customer

java.lang.Object
bcu.cmp5332.bookingsystem.model.Customer
public class Customer extends Object
The Customer class represents a customer in the flight booking system. It contains attributes such as id, name, phone, email, age, and a list of bookings.
